<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    {{> navbar}}

    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="container">
        <p class="heading title">About Us</p>
        <div class="row info">
            <div class="col-7" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="500">
                <p class="heading" >ORIGIN</p>
                <p class="content">Off The Street (OTS) is a clothing line that originated in Balagtas, Bulacan as the result of the ownersâ€™ vision and dream to bring upscale fashion to the streets. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-5" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="500">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591189063234-817139dfe01d?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1351&q=80" class="pic right">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row info">
            <div class="col-5" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="500">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/flagged/photo-1572262009479-12d6def8ad5f?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1080&fit=max&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9" class="pic">
            </div>
            <div class="col-7" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="500">
                <p class="heading">OUR STORY</p>
                <p class="content">We launched this website and started our operations in October 2020 as we aim to deliver fashionable and quality products right at your doorstep. 
                    The people behind OTS are huge fans of streetwear apparel and accessories. The team seeks to showcase the talent of local artists in the country so we are partnering 
                    with them for our designs. With that, Off The Street will be offering fashionable streetwear consisting of t-shirts, pants, jackets, bags, and accessories which are 
                    all locally made. </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="row info">
            <div class="col-7" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="500">
                <p class="content">So are you ready to be part of the team? Let us all conquer the streets in style with Off The Street!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-5" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="500">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530706286591-5d69f83bd514?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1080&fit=max&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9" class="pic right">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

